                            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                            Submit Application
                        </button>
                        <p class="form-note">We'll contact you within 24 hours to discuss next steps</p>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="volunteer-faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <p>Get answers to common questions about volunteering</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-grid">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Do I need any special qualifications to volunteer?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Not necessarily! While some roles may benefit from specific skills, the most important qualifications are enthusiasm, reliability, and a genuine desire to help. We provide training for all volunteers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How much time do I need to commit?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We have opportunities for all schedules! Whether you can spare 1-2 hours per week or several hours per month, we can find something that works for you. Consistency is more valuable than quantity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Is there any training provided?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! All new volunteers attend an orientation session where you'll learn about our mission, meet the team, and receive specific training for your chosen role. Ongoing support is always available.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I volunteer with friends or family?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! Many of our volunteers come as groups or bring family members. It's a great way to bond while making a difference together.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What safety measures are in place?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Volunteer safety is our priority. We provide safety guidelines, never send volunteers to unfamiliar locations alone, and all activities are supervised by experienced staff members.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Will I receive any certificate or recognition?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! We provide volunteer certificates for your records, letters of recommendation when needed, and recognize outstanding volunteers in our annual events and social media.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
